SUMMARY:Jamberry Music with Nicole Jaworski (Co-Sponsored by jBaby)
DESCRIPTION:Join us for joyful\, collaborative music-making with Nicole Jaworski and Jamberry Music! In this class\, you and your little one will bond with each other and make new friends while we sing\, dance\, play\, pretend\, and experiment with instruments. Class is geared to kids 6 months to 2.5 years old\, and siblings are welcome to come! \nClick here to register for this Beth Emet and JUF jBaby class.
