SUMMARY:Soul Stitchers- Knitting Circle in person!
DESCRIPTION:Know how to knit and/or crochet? As a tribute to Nikki Zarefsky z”l\, join us for an hour (on Zoom) of knitting and connecting as we create shawls to warm people during services and/or healing shawls that will bring warmth to those in need in a hospital\, home or other settings. Newcomers are welcome and encouraged to join! Please send us an email with any questions.
