SUMMARY:Beit Sefer
DESCRIPTION:Beit Sefer is an engaging Jewish learning program for learners in Kindergarten through 7th grade. Classes explore Jewish values\, holidays\, Torah stories\, and Hebrew in a supportive and fun environment\, fostering curiosity\, community\, and connection to Jewish life. Learn more about Beit Sefer.
